column1: #Text=Title: Full stack Developer,Position: Full Time...Location: RichField,MN.Salary- $Open(Market) + Benefits + Relocation AssistanceRequirementsJob Description:Position Overview:We are building out an event driven architecture, to connect Marketing source systems.
#Text=They include COTS solutions, SaaS solutions, legacy apps, and custom applications.
#Text=This is being built from the ground up, leveraging Kafka/Rabbit, Java, Cassandra and Microservices built in AWS.

#Text=So, what I am looking for resources with the following qualifications:Java, full stackExperience designing/implementing event driven solutionsMid to senior levelProficient in:Microservices developmentNo SQL (Cassandra)Kafka, RabbitMQOpenShift, Docker and KubernetesCucumberOAuth2.0JunitJenkinsGitFront end experience a plus (React, Angular, etc)Great Communicator (a must)Self-driven, motivated, excited about the workOnsite, 100%Agile/Scrum experienceBenefitsNote: If interested please send your updated resume to muthu.krishnan@two95intl.com and include your salary requirement along with your contact details with a suitable time when we can reach you.

#Text=If you know of anyone in your sphere of contacts, who would be a perfect match for this job then, we would appreciate if you can forward this posting to them with a copy to us.We look forward to hearing from you at the earliest Mid to senior level Microservices development Great Communicator (a must) Self-driven, motivated, excited about the work Salary- $Open(Market) + Benefits + Relocation Assistance
